sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Slack as Slack/Teams
    participant Conn as Connector Framework
    participant Capture as Context Capture Layer
    participant Store as State + Timeline Store
    participant Commit as Commitments
    participant Core as LLM Reasoning Core
    participant Policy as Interaction / Attention Policy
    participant UI as Extension UI

    Slack->>Conn: Message arrives
    Conn->>Conn: Poll or subscribe
    Conn->>Capture: Raw message signal
    Capture->>Capture: Normalize and redact
    Capture->>Store: Append WorkContextEvent
    Commit->>Store: Read candidate event
    Commit->>Core: Extract commitment
    Core-->>Commit: Commitment with confidence
    Commit->>Store: Store commitment
    Store-->>Commit: Provenance ref saved
    Commit->>Policy: Candidate surface
    Policy-->>UI: Propose commitment
    UI-->>Commit: Accept or dismiss
    Commit->>Store: Update status
